    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_llm-raw-scihub-o.O-s00348-005-0004-x.pdf_3_1",
    "text": "Fig. 4 Histogram of measured streamwise (U-component) and cross-stream (V-component) velocities in the illuminated plane",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
